{"tid":1792574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"NOW 新聞做乜撚野事，壽西斯古譯做「齊奧塞斯庫」？！？！？","createTime":"2019-12-21T17:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T17:59:23.000Z","uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cd2f1dfad9490ac094db8c44d5977beac8eb2352","tid":1792574,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T17:54:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=374202\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374202&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3JnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=a720c0d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374202&h=58a9386e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=374202</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】羅馬尼亞紀念暴力革命推翻共產政權三十周年。<br />\n<br />\n羅馬尼亞總統約翰尼斯和多名政府官員在首都布加勒斯特出念儀式，向三十年前參與暴力革命推翻共產政權而喪生的人致敬。另外在革命英雄公墓，亦有民眾掛上聖誕裝飾及獻花，悼念在革命中犧牲的親人。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">羅馬尼亞前總統齊奧塞斯庫</span></strong>領導的共產政權，獨裁統治國家24年，至1989年12月被推翻，歷時9日的暴力革命，造成超過1100人喪生，齊奧塞斯庫及妻子在同年的聖誕節遭處決。"},{"pid":"c18cea558112990385777586c386af4ea135c987","tid":1792574,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T17:57:07.000Z","msg":"【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【行動po】【求推】點解1223去稅局 連登冇人講？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1792093\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1792093</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n點解1223稅局冇人提？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1781990\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1781990</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"htt